AIM:
To create a gliding box using the css animation.

ALGORITHM:
Step 1: First open the vs code or any code editor.
Step 2: Design your gliding box.
Step 3: Type your html code.
Step 4: Then type your css code according to your desire.
Step 5: Execute the file and get the desired output.


CODE:
HTML CODE:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
 <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
 <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
 <div class="card__container">
 <div class="card">
 <h3 class="card__title">SIMILAR POST</h3>
 <P class="card__description">How I recreated a polaroid 
camera with css gradient only</P>
 </div>
 </div>
</body>
</html>

